# Mobile component folders (`many_faces_mobile`)

New UI must live in **colocated folders**, not flat `src/screens/Foo.tsx` or `src/components/Foo.tsx`.

## Rules

- One primary React component = `src/<area>/<Name>/<Name>.tsx` + `index.ts` barrel.
- Import via `@/screens/LoginScreen`, `@/components/AppShell`, `@/components/wall-tickets/WallTicketsSection`, `@/grid/MobilePageLayout`, `@/grid/blocks/BlogGridBlock`, `@/features/settings/SettingsSidePanel`.
- **No** deep imports like `@/screens/LoginScreen/LoginScreen.tsx` from outside the folder.
- Grid block UIs go under `src/grid/blocks/<BlockName>/`; engine stays at `src/grid/` root (`parseGridSchema.ts`, `gridTypes.ts`).
- Cross-cutting non-route UI uses `src/features/<area>/` (mirror portal `features/`).
- Shared hooks stay in `src/hooks/api/`; do not move `httpClient` or contexts into screen folders.

## Before push

From monorepo root:

```bash
node scripts/verify-mobile-component-colocation.mjs
node scripts/verify-mobile-component-colocation.mjs --imports
cd many_faces_mobile && yarn validate
```

Scaffold / batch moves (monorepo root):

```bash
node scripts/colocate-mobile-component.mjs MyScreen --screen
node scripts/colocate-mobile-component.mjs BlogGridBlock --grid-block
node scripts/migrate-mobile-colocate-phase.mjs   # documented phases only
node scripts/fix-mobile-colocated-imports.mjs    # after bulk git mv
```

